description: My HoneyDew this week is Yannis Pappas! Yannis opens up about the deaths of three important people he lost last year. He also tells a story about being shot and how the bullet got lodged in his ass and how the doctor had to remove that bullet. And recently, Yannis fainted on stage and had his entire weekend cancelled. Subscribe, download & review!
